divs: Sighting DetailsI went outside to take my dog out and a reddish egg shaped object flew quickly over my head to the west south west. It was not that big, maybe 10ft by 6 feet and silent. It moved very quickly. I noticed it because my dog was looking at it. It was surprising to see and it freaked me out for quite a few minutes afterward.
